<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨ - <span class="c2">(٢٥٨٧)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6891">يَحْيَى بْنُ أَيُّوبَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">وَقُتَيْبَةُ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4513">وَابْنُ حُجْرٍ </a>قَالُوا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/650">إِسْمَاعِيلُ يَعْنُونَ ابْنَ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4473">الْعَلَاءِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3436">أَبِيهِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">« الْمُسْتَبَّانِ مَا قَالَا فَعَلَى الْبَادِئِ مَا لَمْ يَعْتَدِ الْمَظْلُومُ .»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>